OL,5,G1700 The Chase
OL,6,     FBradley Walsh presents as Phil
OL,7,     Ffrom Nottingham, Hannah from
OL,8,     FOrmskirk, James from Doncaster and
OL,9,     FSally from Gloucestershire pit
OL,10,     Ftheir wits against one of the
OL,11,     Fruthless Chasers in the hope of
OL,12,     Fwinning a potential prize pot
OL,13,     Fworth thousands of pounds. They
OL,14,     Fwork as a team and play
OL,15,     Fstrategically to answer general
OL,16,     Fknowledge questions against the
OL,17,     Fclock and race down the game board
OL,18,     Fto the exit without being caught
