OL,5,G1900 FIFA WC2026: France v Spain
OL,6,     FFrance v Spain (Kick-off 8.00pm).
OL,7,     FCoverage of the first semi-final,
OL,8,     Fwhich takes place at Dallas
OL,9,     FStadium in the USA. The French are
OL,10,     Flooking to reach their third
OL,11,     Fsuccessive final, having finished
OL,12,     Fas runners-up to Argentina in 2022
OL,13,     Fand lifted the trophy in 2018.
OL,14,     FTheir current line-up has arguably
OL,15,     Flooked even more impressive this
OL,16,     Ftime around, and they rarely
OL,17,     Flooked troubled in topping their
OL,18,     Fgroup, before eliminating Sweden,
OL,19,     FParaguay and Morocco in the
OL,20,     Fknockout rounds. Spain reached
OL,21,     Ftheir first World Cup semi-final
OL,22,     Fsince they won the competition in
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
