OL,5,G0300 Noel Edmonds' Kiwi Adventure
OL,6,     FA bout of bad weather is putting
OL,7,     Fincreasing pressure on the
OL,8,     Fviability of Noel and Liz's River
OL,9,     FHaven business as numbers are down
OL,10,     Fdue to the rain, and their
OL,11,     Fboutique vineyard is in danger of
OL,12,     Fsevere frost damage. As the
OL,13,     Fweather improves, Noel is
OL,14,     Fdetermined to turn things round.
OL,15,     FCould raft tours and New Zealand's
OL,16,     Ffirst energy garden help their
OL,17,     Fbusiness survive?
